{"tid":292384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［發泄］如果你件垃圾產品賣唔出？整成Minion咁既樣啦！","createTime":"2017-06-21T10:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T12:45:13.000Z","uid":18720,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe778c959547b074d38b5d264532386b60a6f92","tid":292384,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/183155_b34272183b15d07ffde34f3f6d5a4100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F183155_b34272183b15d07ffde34f3f6d5a4100.jpg&h=d8ceaf59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味閪<br />\n女朋友好撚鐘意minion(我唔撚明呢堆明串緊蝗蟲既黃色生物有乜撚野咁cute)<br />\n一有咩product可以送minion既野 就tag我/lur我去買<br />\n得！tum女咋嘛，之但係次撚次都係一個朝早就比人掃撚晒 買閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如今期e-zone送minion防水袋<br />\n屌你老味又係比人一朝搶晒<br />\n之前minion八達通又係咁 炒到$500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我行左七八間7仔/ok<br />\n連啲5、60歲既呀姐都識發minion呢個音同我講一早賣晒喇<br />\n我就知呢個market真係顛撚左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有冇巴絲可以出讓minion 八達通/防水袋</span>"},{"pid":"d462e40d4408b459a5d7f60ae843159c423cc610","tid":292384,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/184617_5f5bba03292721701137c7ac0f75d9a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F184617_5f5bba03292721701137c7ac0f75d9a5.jpg&h=778ad399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d234dc652e9749a9efad934c7a8801f976338424","tid":292384,"uid":342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"minion condom"},{"pid":"984ec939f5144cf